rows.label: qst501903_msg0002
rows.name:
I've seen careless tourists miss the
mark with 1G or 5G before, but a
whole 500G? That's a first!

rows.label: qst501903_msg0003
rows.name:
Must've been some silly nouveau riche
tourists who never do any exercise.

rows.label: qst501903_msg0004
rows.name:
Though of course, from where we're
standing, they're basically gods!

rows.label: qst501903_msg0005
rows.name:
Dropping blessings of money
from on high! Literally!

rows.label: qst501903_msg0006
rows.name:
Even splitting it between us,
I'll have enough to let my old man
and my sister eat their fill for once!

rows.label: qst501903_msg0007
rows.name: So thank you, whoever you are!
